des:
When you say "Alexa, open Real Secrets" to an Alexa-enabled device, she'll tell you the secrets of real people, sent anonymously to Secrets.  

Every day, you'll hear new secrets that will amaze, delight, or enlighten you. And you can tell your secrets anonymously, too. Just go to Headcanon.com/Secrets.

Who knows? The next secret we select might just be yours.
